msgid "Layouts Disable User Check"
msgstr ""

#: divi-disable-premade-layouts.php:341
msgid ""
"Here you can specify if the user check is disabled. Then the predefined "
"layouts are not displayed for any user of this page."
msgstr ""

#: divi-disable-premade-layouts.php:347
msgid "Layouts Change User Role"
msgstr ""

#: divi-disable-premade-layouts.php:351
msgid ""
"Here you can define with which user role ( hierarchical, e.g. 'editor', "
"'author' etc. ) or which capability ( 'current_user_can( '$cab' ) ) users "
"can access the predefined layouts. Multiple roles or permissions can be "
"entered, separated by commas. The default is set to 'administrator'."
msgstr ""

